[I] Stretch a PDF or raster image across multiple pages

[T] This software allows one to stretch a PDF document or raster image across
[T] multiple pages that can then be printed on a common inkjet or laser
[T] printer, cut and glued together into a larger poster.

[U] https://gitlab.mister-muffin.de/josch/plakativ

